    "body": "If you use the `:latest-unstable` tag for your docker images then you'll pull in the latest patch which includes the TTD\r\n\r\nyou can also use the TTD override flags with v2.3.0:\r\n\r\n* for the beacon node: `--terminal-total-difficulty-override=50000000000000000`\r\n* and for the validator client: `--terminal-total-difficulty-override=50000000000000000`",
